{"tid":2017050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國We Connect！誠邀港人 就「光州 5.18」四十周年傳遞訊息","createTime":"2020-05-15T00:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T15:35:59.000Z","uid":352752,"like":127,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"9430d2376f2cac209842356867569e115c484c94","tid":2017050,"uid":352752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:53:18.000Z","msg":"唔知有人POST咗未 POST咗就由佢啦 想多啲人知道呢件事姐<br />\n同韓國朋友講香港嘅事 佢哋都會諗起光州事件 例如當年軍隊進攻全南大學同朝鮮大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原光州監獄發現&ldquo; 40多具屍體&rdquo; ......可能是5&middot;18失踪者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1790645/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1790645/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國光州電視台短片，對比 1980 光州與今天的香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1817200/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1817200/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就住光州事件同香港抗爭 有咩想同韓國人講 宜家機會黎喇</span> </span><br />\n<br />\nSteve Chung 鍾樂偉<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stevechung413/photos/a.170067379808452/1710800655735109/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstevechung413%2Fphotos%2Fa.170067379808452%2F1710800655735109%2F&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=3b029a48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stevechung413/photos/a.170067379808452/1710800655735109/</a><br />\n<blockquote>下周一，正是 1980 年光州「5.18」民主抗爭運動的 40 周年紀念日。<br />\n<br />\n在別具意義的一年，光州「5.18」紀念活動的主辦單位，希望把當年光州人高舉的民主之火，傳遞到今天的香港人手上。<br />\n<br />\n因而，今天，剛收到了來自光州「5.18」紀念團體的特意傳來的訊息，希望誠意邀請正同樣處於爭取民主抗爭熾熱時期的香港市民，能<span style=\"color: red;\">以各種可行方式（文字訊息、圖片與影片），分享你們對光州「5.18」的感受，及就香港當前抗爭想跟韓國人分享想說的話</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有想跟光州民眾分享訊息（不論任何形式）的朋友，可於本周日（5.17）前，把你的訊息，以私訊跟我傳上。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>周一當在光州「5.18」40 周年紀念日當天，主辦單位會把你們的訊息，張貼在「5.18」紀念委員會網頁之上（<a href=\"http://518people.org/）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F518people.org%2F%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=7b99faa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://518people.org/）。</a><br />\n<br />\n屆時，他們也會透過其臉書專頁，向公眾分享有關訊息。</strong><br />\n<br />\n分享訊息不分語言，中或英都可以。當然，懂韓語的，可以直接把韓語內容跟我傳上呢，謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n誠邀香港人踴躍參與此行動﹗港韓同心，一起抗爭﹗</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7a565952fd586a43a57827b42835b6818c0dc5cb","tid":2017050,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaf84c4edd33ee1325d4613ef069cc4ee0502662","tid":2017050,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:55:05.000Z","msg":"光洲事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c900df2c8600374831840510b722dcd4340afe1b","tid":2017050,"uid":25517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:55:52.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8f885006492fb976af36efc4be483c41c5e09e8e","tid":2017050,"uid":188804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:57:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4e6654051bd0d34cdf2a0c1fd8bb135bc10893f","tid":2017050,"uid":310217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:57:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea7d694cb1981d487a6b82f19de6b2e99bd50c78","tid":2017050,"uid":105090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:57:57.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"744fd1f9cee791492534aaaa570c84c9ebd9fc34","tid":2017050,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:58:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5d6937aa473435b932148fcc600bd18befe024e3","tid":2017050,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:58:37.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"4bcc14e92c6e8c1d8bf50e0471e707640c010304","tid":2017050,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji